  "description": "A dramatic, low-angle shot of a fountain at dusk. The fountain is centrally positioned, with water jets arcing upwards, illuminated by the setting sun behind them. The water creates a shimmering effect and the spray is silhouetted against the bright orange and yellow of the sun. The fountain sits within a large, dark pool surrounded by a paved area. Distant trees and hills are visible in the background, also silhouetted against the warm sky. The overall effect is one of grandeur and tranquility.",
